">69</span></span></a> - R package providing an extensive collection of datasets from agricultural experiments.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/JiaxuanYou/crop_yield_prediction\">Crop Yield Prediction</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/JiaxuanYou/crop_yield_prediction\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">231</span></span></a> - Deep gaussian process for crop yield prediction based on remote sensing data.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/cwfid/dataset\">CWFID</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/cwfid/dataset\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">102</span></span></a> - Dataset comprising field images, vegetation segmentation masks and crop/weed plant type annotations.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/totti0223/deep_learning_for_biologists_with_keras\">Deep Learning for Biologists with Keras</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/totti0223/deep_learning_for_biologists_with_keras\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">76</span></span></a> - Tutorials for deep learning based analysis (mainly) on biological relavent themes.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/danforthcenter/plantcv\">PlantCV</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/danforthcenter/plantcv\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">365</span></span></a> - Plant phenotyping software using computer vision.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://terraref.org\">TERRA REF</a> -> 1PB public domain high resolution sensor data from sorghum breeding trials (<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.5061/dryad.4b8gtht99\">data publication</a> with large files available on <a href=\"https://app.globus.org/file-manager?origin_id=e8feaff4-96cd-11ea-bf90-0e6cccbb0103&#x26;origin_path=%2F\">globus.org at ncsa#terra-public</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"data-standardization-interoperability-and-apis\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#data-standardization-interoperability-and-apis\" aria-label=\"data standardization interoperability and apis permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25